                    </button>
                    <button class="tab-button" data-tab="testimonial-2" role="tab" aria-selected="false">
                        <div class="client-info">
                            <img
                                src="https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/karen-nelson.png"
                                alt="Bonnie Green"
                                class="client-avatar">
                            <div class="client-details">
                                <div class="client-name">Bonnie Green</div>
                                <div class="client-title">CEO at Facebook</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                    <button class="tab-button" data-tab="testimonial-3" role="tab" aria-selected="false">
                        <div class="client-info">
                            <img
                                src="https://flowbite.s3.amazonaws.com/blocks/marketing-ui/avatars/roberta-casas.png"
                                alt="Lana Byrd"
                                class="client-avatar">
                            <div class="client-details">
                                <div class="client-name">Lana Byrd</div>
                                <div class="client-title">CTO at Microsoft</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Testimonial Content -->
            <div class="testimonial-content">
                <div class="testimonial-panel active" id="testimonial-1" role="tabpanel">
                    <div class="quote-icon">❝</div>
                    <h3>It was a great experience!</h3>
                    <p>Working with this team transformed our digital presence completely. Their attention to detail and innovative approach
