                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-panel" id="testimonial-2" role="tabpanel">
                    <div class="quote-icon">❝</div>
                    <h3>Outstanding results!</h3>
                    <p>The level of professionalism and creativity brought to our project was exceptional. Every milestone was met with
                        precision and the final product truly reflects our brand vision.</p>
                    <p>I would recommend this team to anyone looking for top-tier digital solutions. The impact on our business has been
                        remarkable and continues to drive growth.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-panel" id="testimonial-3" role="tabpanel">
                    <div class="quote-icon">❝</div>
                    <h3>Incredible design expertise!</h3>
                    <p>From concept to completion, the design process was seamless and collaborative. The team's ability to translate
                        complex ideas into beautiful, functional solutions is truly impressive.</p>
                    <p>The attention to user experience and technical excellence has set a new standard for our organization. We couldn't be
                        happier with the partnership.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
        const tabButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
        const testimonialPanels = document.querySelectorAll('.testimonial-panel');
        tabButtons.forEach(button => {
            button.addEventListener('click', function () {
                const targetTab = this.getAttribute('data-tab');
                // Remove active class from all buttons and panels
                tabButtons.forEach(btn => {
                    btn.classList.remove('active');
                    btn.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'false');
                });
                testimonialPanels.forEach(panel => {
                    panel.classList.remove('active');
                });
                // Add active class to clicked button and corresponding panel
                this.classList.add('active');
                this.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'true');
                document
                    .getElementById(targetTab)
                    .classList
                    .add('active');
            });
        });
    });
</script>